    "headline": "FICO UK Credit Card Market Report: January 2026",
    "summary": "LONDON, March 23, 2026--Analysis of credit card data for January 2026 by global analytics software leader FICO (NYSE:FICO) shows the typical post-Christmas reduction in spending as customers prioritised payments after the festive break. However, with spending lower year-on-year and increases in missed payments, the financial pressures that were a feature of the UK economy for the majority of 2025 have continued into the new year, requiring risk and collections teams to remain vigilant.",
